l":"mentions"},{"source":"recWw1ssOLYVTdEEM","target":"recmRfnw4XzPBH9jc","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recWw1ssOLYVTdEEM","target":"rec2fX249sj1mmGFr","label":"event"},{"source":"recWw1ssOLYVTdEEM","target":"recVRh2awW5WGpXK4","label":"event"},{"source":"recWw1ssOLYVTdEEM","target":"recQdRNODeVwWG5Qx","label":"event"},{"source":"recWw1ssOLYVTdEEM","target":"recHWkX7SvgnBZiuD","label":"event"},{"source":"recWw1ssOLYVTdEEM","target":"rec78vW2GDruKkctf","label":"event"},{"source":"recWw1ssOLYVTdEEM","target":"rec40p7ak4u60WdPB","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec3bmFSj6sCrwmhp","ref":"Matt.2.1","text":"Now when Jesus was born in Bethlehem of Judaea in the days of Herod the king, behold, there came wise men from the east to Jerusalem,","year":-4},{"id":"rec1Co3AArQU2m6Ha","ref":"Matt.2.2","text":"Saying, Where is he that is born King of the Jews? for we have seen his star in the east, and are come to worship him.","year":-4},{"id":"recK2giqCooj5669M","ref":"Matt.2.3","text":"When Herod the king had heard these things, he was troubled, and all Jerusalem with him.","year":-4},{"id":"recDYWFBBT78nIk7U","ref":"Matt.2.4","text":"And when he had gathered all the chief priests and scribes of the people together, he demanded of them where Christ should be born.","year":-4},{"id":"rec1fYUOeqe8eLeo8","ref":"Matt.2.5","text":"And they said unto him, In Bethlehem of Judaea: for thus it is written by the prophet,","year":-4},{"id":"recdeOlBKFVl2pQxp","ref":"Matt.2.6","text":"And thou Bethlehem, in the land of Juda, art not the least among the princes of Juda: for out of thee shall come a Governor, that shall rule my people Israel.","year":-4},{"id":"reclZ90XU75Kqnpod","ref":"Matt.2.7","text":"Then Herod, when he had privily called the wise men, enquired of them diligently what time the star appeared.","year":-4},{"id":"recNqGE1l48tfnZIF","ref":"Matt.2.8","text":"And he sent them to Bethlehem, and said, Go and search diligently for the young child; and when ye have found him, bring me word again, that I may come and worship him also.","year":-4}]}
